  "text": "And then if, say, an entity daydreams strongly about battling, let us say, another entity, would this occur? I am Ra. In this case the entity's fantasy concerns the self and other-self; this binds the thought-form to the possibility/probability complex connected with the self which is the creator of this thought-form. This then would increase the possibility/probability of bringing this into third-density occurrence.",
